                <note rend="inline" type="source">File No. 893.00/564.</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">The <gloss type="from">American Chargé d’Affaires</gloss> to
                        the <gloss type="to">Secretary of State</gloss>
                    </hi>.</head>
                <opener>
                    <seg rendition="#center">[Telegrams.—Extracts.—Paraphrases.]</seg>
                </opener>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Peking</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1911-10-14">
                            <hi rend="italic">October 14, 1911</hi>
                        </date>.</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>Yuan Shih Kai gazetted Viceroy of Hupeh and Hunan.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Williams.</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
